Description
Sejoy 3-in-1 baby high chair has a multi-function design that it is not only a highchair, but also can be converted into a booster chair or table and chair set. This multi-function baby high chair is suitable for ages from 6 months to 6 years old. It has a user-friendly design, the seat back can be adjusted in 3 positions, and the distance between the tray and the seat back can be adjusted to 3 different sizes to meet the needs of different age groups. Tray is dishwasher-safe and can be removed with one hand to make it easy for feedings, Keep baby safe and comfortable.With a sturdy and durable material that baby high chair ensures safety and ease of use.
Detailed Features
【ASTM and CPC Certified】
Sejoy baby high chairs are passed and meet or exceed all ASTM safety standards and CPC certification standards
【Safe and Reliable Design】
Children's safety and comfort is our top priority. Highchair features a stable pyramid construction and strong materials.
【Removable Double Tray】
the distance between the plates can be adjusted according to the comfort of the child.  
【Adjustable Backrest & Detachable Seat Cushion】
Three-angle adjustable backrest (90°/105°/120°) provides the most comfortable space for your baby's growth.
【Highchair with 3-in-1 Design】
We all know that children grow up so fast, 3-in-1 high chair can witness your child from baby to toddler.
【Simple and Comfortable】
Assembly is easy and comes with detailed instructions, no complicated tools or extra accessories to buy.
